{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"807c6e5bf2","title":"第四部分 反军乱军，破坏部队稳定，阴谋策划组织反革命第二武装","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f65c242c1d","index":0,"year":1984,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"807c6e5bf2"}],"tags":[{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"88958321be","name":"云南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"ad51b2eae3","name":"批林批孔","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"cb691834e6","name":"王必成","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596","name":"刘殷农部份罪行材料（1984.4）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"刘殷农专案组","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/1.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/2.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/3.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/4.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/5.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/6.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/7.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596/8.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/d75a2a91-59b8-4591-ad57-477642c6c596